{"tid":1192332,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"Starfucks d大陸妹好撚嘈","createTime":"2019-06-08T11:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T01:16:13.000Z","uid":237459,"like":1,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a1aa9858d1a2ceee111e95ef1f9a089cd297ca73","tid":1192332,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:17:45.000Z","msg":"諗住星期六去Starbucks 飲咖啡靜下<br />\n點知成堆大陸妹係隔離嘈撚住哂<br />\nD位又窄<br />\n成日係枱同枱中間<br />\n出出入入<br />\n我隻手又放係枱邊等佢patpat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> hi下我手背<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我頂唔順就去拎張紅衫魚<br />\n問佢飲唔飲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我請<br />\n但要幫我我枱底含撚<br />\n<br />\n點知佢話好呀<br />\n我即刻用app叫左杯拿鐵<br />\n之後坐得越來越埋<br />\n大陸唔知係咪興整容<br />\n佢地個個都好厚粉<br />\n整副好撚7既文青眼鏡，但勝在個樣夠後生<br />\n<br />\n唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我一手幫佢放係枱<br />\n之後黎手將佢個頭按近我lin頭位置<br />\n俾佢輕吻我lin<br />\n見佢有少少閪面想後悔<br />\n我獸性又起<br />\n左手輕攬住佢借機抄埋佢左邊波b波微微乳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再按佢落去幫我吹<br />\n<strong>正</strong>佢d口水錫到我成條撚都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔怪得頭先講咁多野<br />\n佢深左幾下後<br />\n我細佬就決定唔理七八九十<br />\n黎手射落佢個口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n射左之後佢好驚咁左遮又遮<br />\n我先施施然去拎杯差唔多凍哂既咖啡<br />\n沖啡條友仲奇怪我就左去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我以勝利之態冷笑一聲<br />\n拎多張紙巾俾條大陸妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf7edab8df41fef711a35e9cc8efd9d2926da43","tid":1192332,"uid":71657,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:19:02.000Z","msg":"入得Starbucks 想靜靜地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你無撚嘢啊.gif"},{"pid":"a097a92cb59353e82cb47fd4f98e1d759fddf8b4","tid":1192332,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9bf7edab8df41fef711a35e9cc8e